title: Tom Brady-Phillip Rivers, playoff outcomes, expectations, & the Blazing 5
itunes:title: Tom Brady-Phillip Rivers, playoff outcomes, expectations, & the Blazing 5
description:
Colin discusses the careers of New England Patriots QB Tom Brady & Los Angeles Chargers QB Phillip Rivers, the most exciting NFL playoff outcomes, what fans expectations should be, and the Blazing 5 picks for the weekend. Guests include DeAngelo Hall, Albert Breer, Eric Dickerson, Greg Jennings, and Jason McIntyre.
